    <lb n="15"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τελευτήσῃ τέκνων αὐτοῖς μὴ ὄντων ἐξ ἀλλήλων ἢ καὶ </supplied><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost"> λ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear>πόντων ἀποδότω Θέων τῷ ταύτης πατρὶ καὶ ἐκ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ότ</supplied>ῃ Χαιρήμονι ἐὰν περιῆι, <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">εἰ</supplied> 

